<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'eno_oblique.css', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to Stochastic Idea Player. Your generated idea is: </h1>
    <p id="answer-container" class="hidden showing ">
      <strong>场景: </strong><%= @idea.city %> &nbsp; <strong>东西: </strong><%= @idea.thing %><br>
      <strong>灵感(Oblique Strategies):</strong>
      <span id='oblique'><%= @idea.oblique %></span>
      <br>
      <strong>丹文(Description):</strong>
      <span id='answer' class="pre-line"><%= @idea.answer %></span>
      <br>
    </p>
    <p>
      To get another one, just follow this link: <%= "http://asky.ideaplayer.shop/" %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>
